<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_242_r1l1">VVir etc <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc daʒ für vns kumen ſind die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l2"><expan>hernachgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns furgelegt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l3">vvie Jn des <expan>Erber<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>veſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Seicʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Marſchalk von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l4">Oberndorff <expan>hauptman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> cʒu höhſtet an der Tunaw helffer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l5">
<add><ab facs="#facs_242_r1l6">vnd geſellen </ab></add> aufgehalten het / mitnamen . Eraſm <expan>Schürſtab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l8">ein vaſʒ mit <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> / <expan>Berhtold<ex>en</ex></expan> kegler 
<del rend="strikethrough">xj </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_242_r1l7">Sechs </ab></add> vaſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l10">groſʒ vnd klein / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_242_line_1577191283564_555">vnd </ab></add> hanſen Craft 
<del rend="strikethrough">iiii </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_242_line_1593417164340_690">j </ab></add> vaſʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">groſʒ vnd </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">klein</del> mit kauffmanſchaft / die Jn derſelbe ~ 
<del rend="strikethrough">Marſchalk </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l12">hauptman gencʒlıch <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd volgen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l13">Als vns dy <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> geſagt vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l14">gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">die ſein vnd <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan></del> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l15">darümb 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hauptmans </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_242_line_1577191322183_568">Jr </ab></add> freunde <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l16">vnd alſo werden vvir des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Seicʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Marſchalks </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l17"><expan>hauptman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> vnd aller ſeiner helffer vnd diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l18">vnd auch aller der die darunter verdaht ſind gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l19">freunde v̈mb die tat <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_242" id="120r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
